  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8cad38374230b7f41bb031b6a4da631d, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "Anyway, I kind of have to feed her chinchilla, but it\u2019s like ok
    if I give it some extra food on the side, yeah? I mean, I don\u2019t know much
    about it, but come on, the woman is ok with letting her cat go outside. And like,
    don\u2019t get me started on how awful video games are for the environment. All
    those batteries and little spare parts\u2026 Should I feed it some chocolate?"
